txt.en: A bounty notice is pinned to the board, stamped with the royal seal of Gondor:\n\n'The Conquest of Gorgoroth requests a brave adventurer to clear Kâm Lagúrz, the Brokencleft of engorged Zhavár-hai. Our dwarf allies are interested in the mineral resources within. Be warned, they are infested with the foul creatures of Lhingris and extremely dangerous.'
The Conquest of Mordor requests an adventurer to handle the engorged Zhavár-hai in Kâm Lagúrz, the Brokencleft.
Engorged Zhavár-hai can be found within Kâm Lagúrz, the Brokencleft.\n\nYou should defeat engorged Zhavár-hai.
